{"tid":461911,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經]一人一個去旅行最刺激經歷","createTime":"2017-11-08T05:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T12:35:04.000Z","uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb1e64688368fd728f6ba94fc34ae95a1904abc","tid":461911,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:31:27.000Z","msg":"有次同個fd去日本旅行,有日去到間成人玩具既鋪頭 入面有隻咩催情朱古力,我地覺得新奇就買左一盒<br />\n<br />\n夜既返到酒店,我同我個fd就諗住試下 點知我地不知不覺咁食左成盒 之後開始黎料,我地下面越黎越硬 開始時大家都只係係床上打j 點知扛極都唔出,反而更想扑野<br />\n<br />\n於是我fd忍唔住想插我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知試左好耐都唔得 之後轉我插佢都插唔入<br />\n<br />\n最後我地69幫大家含到出 完事之後仲攬住訓 到第二日大家就當無事發生過<br />\n<br />\n利申:非gay"},{"pid":"a49b05c590f11a8f8837785e0f9108ceadf911f9","tid":461911,"uid":108236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ching識波"},{"pid":"c3bd85ce072c281d063b04bc247d444ebe60e3e7","tid":461911,"uid":74851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:36:13.000Z","msg":"玩多幾次就悶架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99f2e0cb7a0334512fb632bf054182c88db0c55","tid":461911,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩多幾次就悶架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌屎眼係唔會悶"},{"pid":"d413458523a7d5b910b975ed5309931ecbd102a9","tid":461911,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"自己去吉原同飛田"},{"pid":"36f5eb6ef32c92f628a06ba2f6d873aab83577d0","tid":461911,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:07:33.000Z","msg":"不要再提了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4fdc9